Tga '''Malṭa'''  yat tmazirt igan tagzirt ɣ iffus n urubba. Ism nns unṣib iga t Tagduda n Malṭa (s tmalṭiyt : Repubblika ta' Malta).
Tamaẓunt nns tga tt balita (Valletta). Tutlayin nns tunṣibin gant tnt : tamalṭiyt d tnglizt.
Taggug nn f tuns s 284 km. zdɣn tt 475 000 n umdan.
Tga tamazirt tiss mrawt akk imẓẓyn ɣ umaḍal.

==Tarakalt==
[[Afaylu:EU location MLT.png|thumb|Takarḍa n Malṭa]]
Mqqar tlla Malṭa ɣ [[Urupa]] mac tqqrb ula i [[Tafriqt]].

[[iṭalya|Ṭalyan]] aygan tamazirt iyudsn i Malṭa zɣ tsga n [[Urupa]], d [[Tuns]] d [[Libya]] zɣ tsga n [[Tafriqt]].

Tamazirt ad tsuds zɣ 3 n tgzirin  ituzdɣn nitni : Malṭa, Gudc d Kumuna. d tigzirin ur tuzdɣnin gan : Kumunat ,Filfila, d tgzirt n Umrabḍ bulus.

==Anzwi==
Anzwi n Malṭa iga anzwi n yill Agrakal tanammast n taɣlt tlla gr 12 d 26 tafsna (taskflt) silasyuz (°C), d unẓar itawḍ ar 500 ml ɣ usggwas .

==Imzdaɣ==
Uṭṭun imzdaɣ n Malṭa iga uggar n 400 000 n middn, mac tanẓẓi n middn tmqqur tawḍ ar attayn 1200 n imzdaɣ i Km2, acku tajjuma (surface) n Malṭa tmẓẓiy, tawḍ atayn, 
94% n imzdaɣ n tmazirt ad zdɣn ɣ tmdinin, d ataya n 5% n ibṛaniyn.

==Asgd==
Tamasiḥit aygan asgd unṣib n tmazirt n Malṭa. Mac illa yan wuṭṭun imẓẓiyn n yisgdn yaḍnin.

==Tutlayt==
[[Tutlayt Tamalṭit]] ay-gan tutlayt tunṣibt n Malṭa, nttat tga yat tutlayt tasammit(afru-azyatik) tatrart d atayn 60% zɣ tutlayt a aẓur nns d alatini d  taɛrabt. 
Ar ttaran imalṭiyn tutlayt tamalṭit s agmmay alatin.

